Package Inventory.Model

Class Inventory

java.lang.Object
Inventory.Model.Inventory
All Implemented Interfaces:
IEntity
public class Inventory extends Object implements IEntity
Represents an inventory item in the medical inventory system. Implements IEntity for compatibility with repository operations.
